thread.title: Mrs Dale
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by Mrs Dale

author: Mrs Dale
title: Mrs Dale
text:
Picked up car in Auckland, drove almost 3000 kilometers in 3 weeks, dropped off in Queenstown, no problems whatsoever. I would certainly use this company again.
The car was a Mazda Premacy 2.0 L petrol which was reliable and economical. Plenty of room in the back for 3 large suitcases1 small carry on case and a hold all.
